            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, drain your <strong>green lentils</strong></p><p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in half lengthways, around the stone[s]</p><p>Remove the stone[s] using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh </strong>and slice finely lengthways</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1593437527531-x200.jpg",
