          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Whilst the lentils are cooking, add the <strong>remaining chilli relish</strong> to a bowl along with your <strong>cider vinegar </strong>and 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> and give it a good mix up – this is your <strong>chilli relish dressing</strong></p>",
